101 Uses for Mushrooms by the Mak'a'nor Mining Company.

The recipes contained herein detail many of Jonnic's favourite and most popular uses for the staple crop of the svirfnebli.  Most recipes call for a heartstopping amount of salt but word in the deep says that some surfacers have sampled Jonnic's food and survived!
Thick metal bands encircle the barrel-planks, ensuring a tight seal.
Several piles of 80 pound sacks of pure underdark salt.
The antique drawer pulls are touched by rust and the drawers themselves fit ill within their sockets. It seems the damp air has not been kind to this piece.
You can almost taste the hearty mead within the cask. It looks to have aged well.
